reviewText: God so blessed me when I first discovered this then I wanted everybody I knew to be blessed by such fine worship about the grace and love of God. So awesome.  I have come across what I would call "religious" music that talks about how unworthy we are ,etc., but I want to say I have found Hillsong music to be safe spiritually and full of grace, love and the true gospel of Christ.
